{
  "stem": "323.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- I believe in a supreme being, but I don't believe in organized religion at all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think it's man made.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you're asking my opinion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think all religions are man made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think there is some supreme being.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I'm not an atheist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this supreme being is so horrendous that my little mind could not even under-- begin to understand it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I just feel that it's my-- I have to be responsible to myself and to my conscience.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's my ethics, more than anything else, then that keep me or make me the person I am.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No one knew, basically.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I first came here, I have never seen a black person in my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had always had this idea of this great, free land, with liberty and justice for all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I soon found out differently, boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not the same liberty and justice for all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there never has been.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened in the South.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came in the McCarthy, McCarthy era, and all this was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I couldn't vote yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Adlai-- Adlai Stevenson was running for president, he was this great guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I did, as soon as I could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was stateless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the Germans took away my citizenship after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well so I decided this was going to be my country, I'm going to live here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't think there's a country in the world worth dying for, I can tell you that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I just feel that, if you want to fight, then put all the leaders that want to fight in a circle and let them fight.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just don't believe in war.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
